### Tree Indefication Tool

You can use this simple **Javasctipt** function to indetify a tree by its characteristics:

```
function identify_tree(leaf_shape, region) {if (leaf_shape== "needle" && region == "cold"){ return "Pine Tree" 
} else if (leaf_shape == "broad" && region == "temperate"){ return "Oak Tree"
} else{
  return "Unknown Tree"  
}
console.log (identify_tree("needle", "cold") )
